00:42:25,305 --> 00:42:26,463
<font color="#ffffff">HE CHUCKLES</font>

463
00:42:26,465 --> 00:42:29,423
<font color="#00ff00">We're all rational</font>
<font color="#00ff00">when the sun's shining.</font>

