00:42:57,545 --> 00:42:59,423
<font color="#00ffff">Felt duty bound to buy some jam.</font>

470
00:42:59,425 --> 00:43:02,463
<font color="#00ff00">Want your fortune told?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">No. We're going.</font>

471
00:43:02,465 --> 00:43:04,345
<font color="#00ffff">We just got here. </font><font color="#ffff00">We're going.</font>

