00:48:20,305 --> 00:48:22,543
<font color="#ffff00">He adored her.</font>

505
00:48:22,545 --> 00:48:24,465
<font color="#ffff00">We both did.</font>

506
00:48:26,305 --> 00:48:28,063
<font color="#00ff00">Well...</font>

507
00:48:28,065 --> 00:48:29,985
<font color="#00ff00">..sorry for your loss.</font>

