00:49:03,825 --> 00:49:06,583
<font color="#00ff00">So, have you had any</font>
<font color="#00ff00">thoughts about the list,</font>

517
00:49:06,585 --> 00:49:08,903
<font color="#00ff00">why your name should be on it?</font>

518
00:49:08,905 --> 00:49:13,183
